  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201601/f270161e-8e30-450d-9ecb-643f16d0198d.jpg\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(16,113,181); font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201601/f270161e-8e30-450d-9ecb-643f16d0198d.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 321px;\" /></a><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Beeline\" target=\"_blank\">Beeline</a><br />\n\tA beeline means travelling along a direct route quickly. What is the beeline? Where is the starting point? Where is the destination?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They made a beeline towards... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) make a beeline towards the buffet tables<br />\n\t2) make a beeline for the safe<br />\n\t3) make a beeline for the bed and passes out from exhaustion<br />\n\t4) make a beeline towards the exit<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAs usual, when Doug got to the laboratory building at around midnight, he quickly finished what he was supposed to do. Polishing the floor in the hallway and cleaning the bathrooms did not take long. Then he got down to business and started to do what he was really supposed to do. Double-checking that there was nobody near the premise, he carefully made his way from the chemistry department towards the neuroscience department. He made a beeline towards the office of the team leader of the department, keeping all his senses on high alert.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167051984264/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;